Package com.ibm.struts.taglib.html

Class Summary
FileTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts file tag to adding the dir attribute.
FormTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts form tag to allow creating a Portal link.
PasswordTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts password tag which adds the dir attribute, representing the direction of the text.
SelectTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts select tag to adding the dir attribute.
TextareaTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts textarea tag to adding the dir attribute.
TextTag This class is a simple extension of the Struts text tag to adding the dir attribute.
